Dialogue: 0,0:00:-06.-60,0:00:-03.-02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A world... Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-03.00,0:00:00.-18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A world for you who seek freedom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.-16,0:00:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,stretches out right before your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.01,0:00:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If your endless dreams are your guide,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.01,0:00:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,surpass them, under the flag of your beliefs!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.19,0:00:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Making a splash,\NI've just started on my search
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.69,0:00:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heading towards a world without end
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.20,0:00:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart bursting with enthusiasm,\NI'll go to the ends of the earth
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.37,0:00:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In search of light yet unseen
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.71,0:00:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the summer sun\Nsways the sails of my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.82,0:00:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the cue to open the door to a new world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.33,0:01:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sailing through the rocky waves of despair
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.34,0:01:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We head beyond the horizon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.01,0:01:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Making a splash,\NI've just started on my search
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.68,0:01:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heading towards a world without end
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.19,0:01:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart bursting with enthusiasm,\NI'll go to the ends of the earth
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.36,0:01:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In search of light yet unseen
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.91,0:01:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Pirates' Banquet and\NOperation Escape from Alabasta!"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.75,0:01:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... That compounding is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.25,0:01:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unusual, I might say... Well, it's\Nindeed practical. It's wonderful...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.25,0:01:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.19,0:01:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where on earth did you\Nlearn those medical skills?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.89,0:02:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tony-kun is a doctor from Drum.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.36,0:02:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why! Is that so? The Drum that used to\Nbe the land of advanced medical care...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.20,0:02:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Ahh...!\N--I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.87,0:02:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their medicine is advanced as I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.84,0:02:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been a doctor for 40 years,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.00,0:02:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I didn't know such\Ntechniques existed at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.11,0:02:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Ah...\N--This is really wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.94,0:02:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though you're so young,\NI'm no match for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.62,0:02:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Don't stare at me like that,\Nyou idiot! Go away, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.49,0:02:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Well, have some tea and watch as much\Nas you like"... Can I take it that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.99,0:02:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.16,0:02:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... really, you're outstanding!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.73,0:02:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.13,0:02:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can only say I'm impressed.\NBoy oh boy, you've got splendid skills!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.37,0:02:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go away! Shut up, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.25,0:02:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Do you have more lumber?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.58,0:02:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have enough, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.75,0:02:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got some extra. Go ahead and use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.95,0:03:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.42,0:03:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This country is sturdy...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.16,0:03:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because the princess is cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.06,0:03:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--That has something to do with it?\N--It does!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.59,0:03:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! House after house is penetrated!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.63,0:03:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this hole? It looks as if\Nsomeone kicked and broke them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.16,0:03:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Urk!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.20,0:03:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time to go around!\NI'll take a shortcut!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.30,0:03:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! This is terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.47,0:03:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Usopp! Look!\NThere's something over there...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.74,0:03:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.78,0:03:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll improve my concentration...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.22,0:03:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until I can bring out that power any time...\NI can't consider myself stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.32,0:03:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa... They're all interesting books!\NIs it really okay to take them with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.56,0:03:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's fine, since I've read all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.87,0:03:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you! Then I'll help myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.14,0:03:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you not hear me say\NI don't know?! Go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.27,0:03:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you lie, it'll harm your country!\NSheltering pirates is a felony.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.21,0:03:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey, what's up?\N--Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.31,0:04:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.71,0:04:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think we were able to purchase enough,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.08,0:04:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--considering the state this city is in...\N--Do you have any evidence\Nthat pirates are here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.88,0:04:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yeah...\N--Do you have any evidence\Nthat pirates are here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.05,0:04:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.12,0:04:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if he woke up...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.09,0:04:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he wakes up, things'll get noisy, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.02,0:04:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy... I slept really well!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.46,0:04:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? My hat? My hat! Where's my hat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.10,0:04:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starving! Breakfast! Hey, breakfast!\NWhere's my hat?! Breakfast! My hat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.94,0:04:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just woke up and you're already loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.31,0:04:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it won't be breakfast.\NIt's early evening right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.18,0:04:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your hat is over there. A soldier found\Nit for you in front of the palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.25,0:04:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, good!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.58,0:04:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you got well, Luffy-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.92,0:04:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got well? I've always been well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.52,0:04:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dummy! You were in serious\Ncondition with a high fever and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.49,0:04:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vivi and Chopper attended you all this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.79,0:04:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.40,0:04:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh hey, Luffy! You woke up?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.07,0:04:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Zoro, long time no see!\N"Long time no see"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.27,0:04:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh, hey! You went out\Ntraining again, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.04,0:05:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? It's my business, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.81,0:05:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No means no! I'm the ship doctor!\NAnd don't take off the bandages, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.04,0:05:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to move with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.48,0:05:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.31,0:05:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Long time no see"...? "Long time no see"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.68,0:05:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's probably natural to feel\Nthat way... since you slept for three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.05,0:05:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three days?! Did I sleep\Nfor three whole days?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.32,0:05:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.73,0:05:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I missed 15 meals...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.36,0:05:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How come you can calculate so\Nquickly when it comes to food?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.50,0:05:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, in his calculations\Nthere are five meals a day!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.43,0:05:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I hear right that the captain is up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.43,0:05:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be dinner time soon,\Nso would you wait a little?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.30,0:05:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Wha...?!\N--Oh hey, old tube-hair guy! You're alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.04,0:05:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S... So you really were\Ninto that sort of thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.44,0:05:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, everyone. She's Terracotta-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.41,0:05:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's Igaram's wife and is also\Nthe head of the palace's servers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.35,0:05:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for helping\NVivi-sama and my husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.55,0:05:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...! A wife could resemble\Nher husband, but this is too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.62,0:05:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you eat a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.72,0:05:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you have some fruit to\Nhold you over until dinner time?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.16,0:05:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.33,0:05:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a magician?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.79,0:05:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady, I'm gonna eat\Nthree days worth of food!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.66,0:06:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looking forward to it! I've devoted\Nmy past 30 years to the job of serving!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.27,0:06:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't lose against a youngster's stomach,\Nso eat to your heart's content!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.64,0:06:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They don't have a shred of dignity...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.81,0:06:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meals at this dining hall are\Nsupposed to be quieter than this...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.68,0:06:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, it wasn't an empty boast.\NBut I won't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.22,0:06:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat quick or it'll be gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.69,0:06:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Luffy! You just took the\Nfood from my plate, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.53,0:06:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't spit the food!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.86,0:06:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey hey, if you eat in\Na hurry like that, you'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.33,0:06:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got a lot, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.73,0:06:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, wait and see, Luffy.\NI'll put the Tabasco Star on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.04,0:06:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! When did you...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.94,0:06:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you call that dish?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.34,0:06:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is called konafa. You bake\Nnoodles in the oven and...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.48,0:06:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.15,0:06:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, here's more!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.98,0:06:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Off man, I diffn mow mu mere meh ming!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.32,0:06:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Men mu're... muff... Mimi's mad, muh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.52,0:06:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well... we can talk after the dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.72,0:07:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meah, mu're might.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.26,0:07:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I have another mug full?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.06,0:07:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, we need some water here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.63,0:07:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a noisy dinner table...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.80,0:07:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're too vulgar to keep watching...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.61,0:07:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can Vivi-sama just keep laughing...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.37,0:07:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Whoa!\N--This is the palace's proud main bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.51,0:07:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We normally use this only\Nduring the rainy season.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.21,0:07:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing! This is gorgeous! Gorgeous!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.31,0:07:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'll be the first to go in!\N--No, I'll be the first!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.45,0:07:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you guys enjoying that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.05,0:08:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I really enjoyed the dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.82,0:08:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of the current situation,\NI thought we'd keep it simple,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.92,0:08:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it seems that anything you guys\Nget involved with would become a party.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.13,0:08:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Zoro, look at this! We can train here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.80,0:08:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Training! Training!\N--What training is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.40,0:08:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So where's the women's bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.33,0:08:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you nuts?! Why would I tell you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.30,0:08:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vivi-sama's there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.77,0:08:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so stingy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.87,0:08:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's behind that wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.31,0:08:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,King! You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.88,0:08:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, old guy! You're not bad at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.65,0:08:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This feels good! I wonder if a ship\Nwith a big bath like this exists...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.05,0:08:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it does, since the sea is so vast.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.92,0:08:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We saw giants... We saw dinosaurs...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.76,0:08:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We also saw cherry blossoms\Nbloom in a winter land...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.63,0:08:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There're more and more things in the\Nsea that are beyond our imagination!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.27,0:08:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Well...\N--It's my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.84,0:08:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.00,0:08:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.54,0:08:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what're you all doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.77,0:08:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those idiots...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.18,0:09:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be 100,000 berries per person, okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.65,0:09:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.65,0:09:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happiness Punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.95,0:09:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.02,0:09:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mellorine...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.49,0:09:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't make up your mind, can you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.06,0:09:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.06,0:09:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thinking that we might\Nwanna leave here tonight...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.50,0:09:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.80,0:09:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because we no longer have\Na reason to stay here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.40,0:09:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Navy is probably at the\Nharbor ready to capture us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.97,0:09:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our ship will be in danger soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.08,0:09:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.45,0:09:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You dirty old man...\N--I'm not talking about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.39,0:09:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm talking about the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.53,0:09:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey hey, is it okay... for a\Nking to do such a thing...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.67,0:09:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a serious incident, Cobra-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.17,0:10:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A king shouldn't bow his head to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.21,0:10:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Igaram... Authority is something\Nyou wear over your clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.88,0:10:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we're in the bath. There isn't\Nsuch a thing as a naked king.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.68,0:10:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to thank you from\Nthe bottom of my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.42,0:10:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as a father and as a resident of this land.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.90,0:10:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.00,0:10:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really appreciate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.21,0:10:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Tonight?!\N--That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.28,0:10:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leaving here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.14,0:10:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I think it's appropriate, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.88,0:10:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,since we no longer have\Na reason to stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.12,0:10:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... I'm also worried\Nabout the Navy's actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.72,0:10:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then. You decide, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.49,0:10:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! We'll leave after we have\Nsome more Alabasta dishes again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.69,0:10:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're leaving right away, idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.09,0:10:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Idiot!\N--You don't all have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.96,0:10:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do, Igaram-san?!\NWe have to let them know right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.56,0:11:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, of course. But...\Nthis is becoming a big deal...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.77,0:11:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope they can leave this island safely...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.44,0:11:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How quickly they prepared...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.77,0:11:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roronoa Zoro. His bounty\Nis 60 million berries!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.94,0:11:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey D. Luffy. His bounty\Nis 100 million berries!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.85,0:11:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Igaram-san...\N--With bounties of this level,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.22,0:11:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,flag officers at Navy Headquarters\Nwill surely start taking actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.16,0:11:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can no longer go back, Luffy-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.49,0:11:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You and your crew took down one pillar\Nof the Seven Warlords of the Sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.35,0:11:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.06,0:12:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vivi-sama, where are they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.79,0:12:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Igaram? What's the big hurry?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.60,0:12:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did Luffy-kun and the others go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.90,0:12:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To the sea... They're pirates, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.24,0:12:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.41,0:12:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, you guys. Pirates are scum.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.17,0:12:18.22,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Navy Headquarters Sergeant,\NJango the Traitor"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.24,0:12:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what're you saying?\NDon't you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.84,0:12:21.46,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Navy Headquarters Sergeant,\NIron Fists Fullbody"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.48,0:12:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You used to be a pirate, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.02,0:12:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Urk! That's right! You're exactly right, baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.49,0:12:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna dance?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.82,0:12:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh! Yeah! Dance! Dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.46,0:12:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dance! Dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.70,0:12:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like those two took down\Nthe enemy ship and returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.83,0:12:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It took them forever.\NI wonder what they were doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.17,0:12:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I put trust in their ability and left the\Nship we were attacking in their hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.31,0:12:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Disappointed. I'm disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.11,0:12:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you finished deploying the ships?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.71,0:12:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am! It's perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.41,0:12:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've completely blocked\Nevery harbor in the country!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.98,0:12:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--However...\N--Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.95,0:13:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's just one thing\NI'm concerned about...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.82,0:13:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.82,0:13:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About the Straw Hats' ship that I\Nthought we confirmed in Erumalu...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.53,0:13:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.53,0:13:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me they've\Nalready left this country...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.36,0:13:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... I don't think that's the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.10,0:13:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then search for it... every corner of the coast!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.63,0:13:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am! Will do!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.23,0:13:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Geez...\N--Miss Hina! Sorry it took so long!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.70,0:13:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please ask us why it took so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.91,0:13:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did it take so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.68,0:13:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--We were picking flowers... for you...!\N--Don't need them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.01,0:13:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man your positions right away!\NWe'll take down the Straw Hat gang!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.45,0:13:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Straw Hats?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.75,0:13:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmmm... This is nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.76,0:13:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is finally farewell\Nto the sand kingdom...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.23,0:13:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Luffy, when are you gonna stop eating?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.99,0:13:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Alabasta dishes are great!\NSanji, make them sometime...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.76,0:13:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I was interested, too, so I got\Nsome recipes from Terracotta-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.63,0:13:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some spices, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.04,0:13:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami, are you feeling sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.27,0:14:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami, do you want one piece\Nof meat? Just one piece, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.18,0:14:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san, you're thinking\Nabout Vivi-chan, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.55,0:14:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand how you're feeling...\Nbut thinking doesn't get you anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.65,0:14:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I know... you two were really close...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.39,0:14:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But hey... chin up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.56,0:14:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.57,0:14:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For Vivi's sake... I'm willing to give up...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.74,0:14:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...on the 1 billion berries...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.97,0:14:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Of course you should!\N--So it was about money?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.78,0:14:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Usopp fell!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.24,0:14:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami! Don't act misleading!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.58,0:14:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What're you guys worked up about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.75,0:14:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's about Vivi, it's no use\Nworrying about it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.12,0:14:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Usopp fell!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.75,0:14:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave him be.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.36,0:14:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.12,0:14:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Karoo! Where are you, Karoo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.00,0:14:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use, Igaram.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.50,0:14:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? We should at least let them\Nknow their current situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.13,0:14:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I had the Duck Squadron\Ntake them, even Karoo can't catch up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.97,0:15:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it won't change anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.31,0:15:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What won't change?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.84,0:15:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll be happy when they know it.\NThat's all. Nothing will change.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.04,0:15:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--But...!\N--They'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.58,0:15:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, leave! I'm going to bed!\NYou have to get up early, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.62,0:15:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... yes. That's right. We have to let\Nthe entire country hear your voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.49,0:15:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know. Come here, Karoo.\NLet's sleep together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.33,0:15:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hmm...\N--Igaram-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.53,0:15:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something's bothering me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.94,0:15:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.67,0:15:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's too calm... Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.21,0:15:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Strange... There's something strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.19,0:15:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's quiet, isn't it, Karoo?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.86,0:15:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't had a quiet night\Nlike this for a long time...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.96,0:15:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The cook who fights with\Nthe fridge robber is gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.40,0:16:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The swordsman who trains\Nevery night is also gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.67,0:16:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The navigator who throws her\Npillow half asleep is gone, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.70,0:16:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.24,0:16:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Transponder snail\Ncommunication? From who?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.81,0:16:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From someone named Bon-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.61,0:16:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bon-chan? Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.08,0:16:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one knows him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.62,0:16:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he insists he's your friend, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.55,0:16:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.02,0:16:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello? Hi there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.76,0:16:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me! Me! Uhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.23,0:16:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.20,0:16:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's you, huh?\NWhat do you want from us?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.70,0:16:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? That voice must be Straw Hat, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.97,0:16:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're strong! I was so surprised!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.14,0:16:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah... Don't call me Mr. 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.38,0:16:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this signal is caught by\Nthe Navy, I'll be in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.48,0:16:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just said it yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.32,0:16:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just tell us what you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.72,0:16:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah... I took your ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.29,0:16:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.52,0:17:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You son of a bitch! This isn't a\Njoking matter! Where're you now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.13,0:17:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On your ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.23,0:17:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of all others, he...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.76,0:17:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no...! Gee...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.60,0:17:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're friends, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.24,0:17:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's at the upper reaches\Nof the Sandora River...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.28,0:17:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we trust him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.62,0:17:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We became friends one time, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.98,0:17:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In your case, you may be able to make\Nfriends with him again, which is scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.59,0:17:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we have no choice but to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.32,0:17:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right. He has our ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.56,0:17:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he tries to trick us,\Nthen we'll just beat him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.99,0:17:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that it's decided, let's get ready quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.73,0:17:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Let's hurry. If we don't\Nget there quickly, our ship will...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.80,0:17:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.87,0:17:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say... everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.84,0:17:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What... should I do...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.38,0:17:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen well, Vivi. We'll give you 12 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.28,0:18:00.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Current Location: Alubarna"\N"Nanohana" "Sandora River"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.02,0:18:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once we take our ship\Nback on the Sandora River,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.89,0:18:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll draw the ship near the eastern harbor\Njust once at exactly noon tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.36,0:18:07.71,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Eastern Harbor"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.73,0:18:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We probably won't be able to anchor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.76,0:18:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to continue traveling with us,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.86,0:18:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that moment is the only\Nchance to come aboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.17,0:18:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that happens, we'll welcome you...\Nthough you'll become a pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.34,0:18:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you're a princess of a country,\Nthis is the best we can do to invite you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.34,0:18:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come, Vivi! Definitely come! Come now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.84,0:18:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Stop it, Luffy.\N--Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.91,0:18:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?! Don't you want her to come?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.08,0:18:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the point!\NIt's something Vivi has to decide!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.92,0:18:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noon tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.29,0:18:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's the eastern harbor, it'll take\Nfour hours to get there on Karoo...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.00,0:18:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I leave here at 8, I'll make it on time...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.10,0:18:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never thought of becoming a pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.17,0:19:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I miss this chance, I'll never have\Nsuch a choice for the rest of my life...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.88,0:19:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never thought that being\Na princess was uninteresting,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.38,0:19:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the country is still at a critical point,\Nthough the rebellion is over...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.72,0:19:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I go, you'll go too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.00,0:19:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say... Karoo...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.10,0:19:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What... would you like to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.27,0:19:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.51,0:19:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.68,0:19:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.84,0:19:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, unload! Thanks, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.15,0:19:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to say goodbye to you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.05,0:19:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have a safe trip back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.58,0:19:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say hello to the King, the old\Ntube-hair guy and the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.45,0:19:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.49,0:19:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll see you... definitely\Nsee you again someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.70,0:19:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Wait a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.53,0:19:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What?!\N--Don't "what" me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.83,0:20:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not how you should\Ntreat your friend, is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.04,0:20:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean "friend"?\NWe were enemies. You lied to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.61,0:20:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't lie! I didn't know it, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.48,0:20:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you see... who cares about it anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.25,0:20:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Baroque Works fell. We're no longer enemi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.45,0:20:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey, move over...\N--Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.49,0:20:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we're not enemies,\Nwhy are you on our ship?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.13,0:20:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You stupid head!\N--What'd you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.63,0:20:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen! If I wasn't on this ship now,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.03,0:20:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what do you think would've happened to it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.97,0:20:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It might've been taken by the Navy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.94,0:20:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What?!\N--It's not "might've"!\NIt definitely would've happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.94,0:20:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what's going on\Naround this island right now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.61,0:20:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's completely blocked by\Nthe Navy ships! It's blocked!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.61,0:20:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Then you protected\Nthe Going Merry from the Navy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.78,0:20:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Why?!\N--How come?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.88,0:20:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because we're friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.59,0:20:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do we still have stuff to load?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.59,0:20:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope. This is the last one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.43,0:21:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, Mr. 2...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.13,0:21:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys couldn't get off of the\Nisland due to the Navy's coast siege,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.24,0:21:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so you wanted to find allies...\NIsn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.67,0:21:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bon-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.27,0:21:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right... In a time like this...\NBecause it's a time like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.58,0:21:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gather! In the name of friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.64,0:21:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's unite our strength and fight together!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.51,0:21:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.72,0:21:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.42,0:21:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.82,0:21:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, thanks in advance!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.32,0:21:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.49,0:21:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Hina! Miss Hina!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.16,0:21:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We found it! We found the Straw Hats' ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.90,0:21:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near the upper reaches of the Sandora River!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.50,0:21:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.75,0:21:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which direction should I run towards\Nto see a more wonderful tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.89,0:22:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I took the helm and opened the\Nmiraculous map that I stored in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.66,0:22:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I aimed for the sky and sought out\Nmy dreams, though at times I got lost
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.87,0:22:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't a dream; when I met you,\NI discovered the wonderful person in me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.31,0:22:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With just a bit of courage,\NI gained something grand
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.51,0:22:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's the time for my "wish"\Nto become my "pledge"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.85,0:22:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shining ray! Find your brand new way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.79,0:22:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's sketch out the tale of the future
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.89,0:22:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll put all my feelings\Nin a brand new wind now
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.80,0:22:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shining ray! Find your brand new way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.77,0:22:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A never-ending journey to be together
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.94,0:22:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll chase after you\Nwherever you go, Shining ray
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.48,0:22:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vivi will come, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.78,0:22:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Adventures are fun.\NThere's no way she won't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.98,0:23:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give up, Luffy. Her case\Nis different from ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.12,0:23:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, this is bad! The Navy\Nis following us again!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.49,0:23:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way she won't come!\NShe'll be a pirate with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.89,0:23:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father... Igaram... I have something\Nimportant to talk with you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.63,0:23:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.93,0:23:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"It All Started on That Day!\NVivi Tells the Story of Her Adventure!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.07,0:23:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
